{"type": "article", "id": 2231, "title": "咖啡机闹钟", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:18:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052222583yulk72XcaOzQE4n.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">谁不希望早上一睁开双眼就有一杯煮好的咖啡送到枕边？独居的同学们现在也可以想想这种好事了。伦敦设计师 Josh Renouf 设计了一款闹钟+咖啡机组合，头天晚上设定好闹钟，第二天清晨到点咖啡机就开始工作，当咖啡香气弥漫在房间里，你也被唤醒了，想到一杯新鲜烫嘴的咖啡在等着你，还怎么有心思继续赖在床上呢？</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135123LT8b9sRgGIJ5U40V.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135124xt7FMKc3mC2RDkai.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135125msWTBU734dL8DzNw.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}